{"tid":1803971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲封殺華為另覓公司發展 5G　Vodafone 和記選 Nokia 合作","createTime":"2019-12-30T15:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T02:47:29.000Z","uid":28114,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8520c622542d087ebbf2486e8d5975158869b7dd","tid":1803971,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1523167459-5g-getty.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F1523167459-5g-getty.jpg&h=74267226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在去年 8 月的時候，澳洲政府以國家安全為由就禁止了華為在當地提供 5G 網絡技術及零件，希望物色其他公司以提供有關的技術。近日，外媒就報導指英國電信商 Vodafone 與和記電信澳洲有限公司組成的寬頻服務合資企業已經與 Nokia 諾基亞達成協議，共同研發並在澳洲推出 5G 服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/25880292704_ad2686596b_k-1536x1017.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F25880292704_ad2686596b_k-1536x1017.jpg&h=00348187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據外媒透露，Vodafone 與和記電信澳洲在今日發佈了聯合聲明，表示他們的合資企業 Vodafone Hutchison Australia 將會與諾基亞合作，由後者在當地成為網絡供應商，為當地打造 5G 網絡，預計最快 2020 年上半年開始可以推出。<br />\n<br />\nVodafone CEO 就表示選擇諾基亞的原因是因為對方提出了令人信服的 5G 技術路線圖，與他們對 5G 的目標一致，在考慮後就決定與他們合作。除此之外，諾基亞亦表示在是次合作中將會協助 Vodafone 改善當地所提供的 4G 網路，希望提供更穩定的網絡予澳洲用戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/12/30/vodafone-australia-to-deploy-a-nokia-based-5g-network/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F12%2F30%2Fvodafone-australia-to-deploy-a-nokia-based-5g-network%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=f1d726c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/12/30/vodafone-australia-to-deploy-a-nokia-based-5g-network/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"b495c6fac6bd248798814483fba9a778bf446652","tid":1803971,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=520691ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=09f0c1be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要29000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=7c805592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>美國聯署</ins> deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">3/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要7000人 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=ffc5adde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-c